data.description:
Presenting to you is a huge two family home that needs some TLC. Great for an investment property. Located in the heart of the thriving Brownsville section of Brooklyn, and close to all. Just minutes from Downtown Brooklyn and Manhattan. 
Features Includes:
Apt. #1- 3.5 bedrooms, kitchen, living space, 1 full bathroom, wood floors, closet space, vaulted ceilings, private yard & deck.
 Apt. #2- 3.5 bedrooms, kitchen, living space, 1 full bathroom, wood floors, closet space, vaulted ceilings, private terrace.
 Basement- Private entrance- Full basement- unfinished- huge possibilities for rental income.
